import React from "react"

const SearchItem = (search,setSearch) => {
  return (
    <form className='searchForm' onSubmit={(e) => 
    e.preventDefault()}>
        <lable htmlFor="search"></lable>
        <input
            id='search'
            type="text"
            role='searchbox'
            placeholder='Search Items'
        />
    </form>
  )
}

export default SearchItem
